                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I get this EC LDoN yesterday on my enchanter, shes 57, and I tell the group before we go in...
<br />

<br />
"I am a chaming enchanter, That means that I charm a mob and make it my pet for teh duration of this romp. I know how to handle my pet, I only need a heal once and again. So when it breaks and startes beating on me LET IT! Thank you, <bows>"
<br />

<br />
We go in, I make my pet and we are fine for awile, then he breaks and starts beating on me. No problem, I mezz it, retash it, recharm it, and tell it to follow me... We move alog and eventually It breaks again. This time, instead of leving it Be LIKE I TOLD THEM TO! The warrior Rushes it and Breaks the Mezz and gets me killed.. Not a big deal, I think, when I get rezzed back I will warn them about it and we can continue. I get back loot my stuff and as I'm medding up the warrior say "ok, no more pets." 
<br />

<br />
I'm like WTF you an idiot or something!? YOUR the reason I died. NOT my abilitie to deal with my pet... I SAY "Ok. Fine! you want to lose alot of DPS because YOU can't deal with my having a pet thats fine."  
<br />

<br />
Was the most Boreing adventure I've had in a long time.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=904458" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: red">Illusionist Qilue Mansbane</span></a>  
